a-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Jan 08, 2025</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104dzy1665702618507.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/dzy1665702618507.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/dzy1665702618507.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"dzy1665702618507\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      Hyperlink\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">This property determines whether the widget behaves as a hyperlink (<code class=\"ph codeph defvalue\">True</code>; default) or a dynamic label <code class=\"ph codeph\">False</code>.\n </p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"dzy1665702618507__p_d104744e1_d104745e1_d104746e1\">hyperlink<code class=\"ph codeph\">=</code><code class=\"ph codeph\">\"</code><code class=\"ph codeph defvalue\">True</code> | <code class=\"ph codeph\">False</code><code class=\"ph codeph\">\"</code></p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"dzy1665702618507__table_d12368e1_d12369e1_d12370e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"dzy1665702618507__table_d12368e1_d12369e1_d12370e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Value</p>\n</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"dzy1665702618507__table_d12368e1_d12369e1_d12370e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Description</p>\n</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"dzy1665702618507__table_d12368e1_d12369e1_d12370e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph defvalue\">True</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"dzy1665702618507__table_d12368e1_d12369e1_d12370e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">The cursor changes to a pointing hand when resting on the widget, and the Detail trigger is executed when the user clicks on the widget.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"dzy1665702618507__table_d12368e1_d12369e1_d12370e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">False</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"dzy1665702618507__table_d12368e1_d12369e1_d12370e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">The Detail trigger and the hand cursor are disabled. This mimics a transparent, dynamic label at run time.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"dzy1665702618507__section_yns_2kd_xwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d688956e139\">Example: Setting in ProcScript</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"dzy1665702618507__p_d104750e1_d104751e1_d104752e1\">The following code changes the behavior and text of\n            a hyperlink so that it cannot be perform the action defined by the\n               <span class=\"keyword\">Detail</span> trigger.</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"dzy1665702618507__pre_exx_fkd_xwb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">$fieldproperties(FLD) = \"hyperlink=false\"\nFLD = \"Not available\"</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"dzy1665702618507__section_hm1_hkd_xwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d688956e154\">Applies To</h2>\n<p class=\"p\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"hta1665703126401.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/hta1665703126401.html\" title=\"The uhyperlink widget is a display-only widget that acts like a hyperlink in a web page. It activates a command when the user clicks it. It can only be used in form components. Uniface provides a logical widget called Hyperlink, which is mapped to uhyperlink.\">uhyperlink (Hyperlink)</a></p>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3612716\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3612716\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Hyperlink Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Jan 08, 2025 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Hyperlink This property determines whether the widget behaves as a hyperlink ( True ; default) or a dynamic label False . hyperlink = \" True | False \" Value Description True The cursor changes to a pointing hand when resting on the widget, and the Detail trigger is executed when the user clicks on the widget. False The Detail trigger and the hand cursor are disabled. This mimics a transparent, dynamic label at run time. Example: Setting in ProcScript The following code changes the behavior and text of a hyperlink so that it cannot be perform the action defined by the Detail trigger. $fieldproperties(FLD) = \"hyperlink=false\" FLD = \"Not available\" Copy Applies To uhyperlink (Hyperlink) Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}